  <scopecontent id="aspace_a0c688d085f7a5a2b07e7a94069c14c3">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Includes photographs, mostly of fraternity members; pamphlets about the fraternity; records of the fraternity's Building Fund Campaign; and other correspondence and miscellaneous records of Theta Delta Chi at Cornell University. Also includes scrapbooks kept by Luzerne Coville (Class of 1886) and Charles Rodman Stull (Class of 1907); and copies of the chapter newsletter, The Beta Bulletin, 1981-2015.</p>  </scopecontent>
